Registration form 
===================

+ Introduction 

This is the first version of the registration form created using HTML5. It adds logic where different types of IDs can be entered and validated. The simple validation involved requires a user to re-enter the details inserted into a field that requires validation.

+ How to add a validated field

To add a input field type that is to be validated, 

1. Insert the field type 'div'
   <div id="..." class="...">
	<label for="...">{name of id}</label>
	<input class="need_validation" id="..." name="..." type="text">
	<span class="alert_message"></span>
    </div>

## If the input field requires validation, add the 'need_validation' class to the input type 
## add the '<span class="alert_message"></span>' section. This is where the error messages will be displayed
